cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.IT, cs.CC

The paper discusses the challenges and improvements in delivering multimedia streaming services over wireless and mobile networks, which involves network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also focuses on the user experience and the measurement of Quality of Experience (QoE), which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses controlling approaches and enhancements proposed by researchers, which could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper also mentions the need for Quality of Service (QoS), which is related to cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
